<plot>A young couple on the first night of their honeymoon spontaneously engage in a "Game," whereby the young woman takes on the pretend role of a seductive hitchhiker, and the young man takes on the role of a stranger. The "Game," which begins playfully, turns out to have dire consequences in irrevocably transforming the relationship between the husband and wife.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?564636</url></doc>
